➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：梅花命
http://www.sohu.com/a/438022327_100115135	45571
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201213/9fa8cbcea5644341a3c728af807d8d2d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>梅花命</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣（武汉）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梅花命，注定我孑然一身</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">走在季节中，寒冷权当风衣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凌冽刺骨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风鞭子抽打过脸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">猝不及防的际遇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都会在趔趄中无语凝噎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每当缓过一气，枝杆都会上长一寸硬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你可见磨冰枝头开出红花</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有血液奔腾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有我的生命在绽放啊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写于2020年12月12日下午</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201213/917d90fc43f34c43a61fdd6515364878.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
