➜苏坛：《消失的村庄》
http://www.sohu.com/a/438022937_100115135	46068
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201213/2fec292e756a486d9f37aad68daf9b6d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《消失的村庄》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那片芦苇荡还在寒风中摇曳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那座村庄已经荡然无存</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我再也看不见那村口的栓马石</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不会再走过那印着毛主席万岁的大会堂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>曾经贯通东西的悠悠村巷</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>古老而久远</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>走出过英雄和科学家</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也走进过日本鬼子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我的老祖母也曾经撑过摆渡船</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我走过的那间砖瓦老屋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有吸鸦片的榻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我曾经住在那里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过昨天发生的事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已经成为记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201213/47830fb41c664012a9cc68ede1d0b892.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
